official_title: To amend title XVIII of the Social Security Act to provide for coverage under the Medicare program of pharmacist services.
short_title: Pharmacy and Medically Underserved Areas Enhancement Act

summary.text:
Pharmacy and Medically Underserved Areas Enhancement Act

Amends title XVIII (Medicare) of the Social Security Act to cover pharmacist services.
